<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.7.1">
<l>māṉa muṭaittuṅka ḷāyar kulamata ṉālpiṟar makkaḷ tammai</l>
<l>yūṉa muṭaiyaṉa ceyyap peṟāyeṉ ṟirappa ṉurappa killēṉ</l>
<l>nāṉu muraittilēṉ nantaṉ paṇittilaṉ naṅkaikāḷ nāṉeṉ ceykēṉ</l>
<l>tāṉumōr kaṉṉiyum kīḻai yakattut tayirkaṭai kiṉṟāṉ pōlum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “Your herder clan has honor; therefore, you do not get to do</l>
<l>Disgraceful things to others’ children,” I  beg [him]. I am not able to be firm.</l>
<l>And I do not speak up. Nanda does not command [him]. Ladies, what can I do?</l>
<l>It seems like he is churning curds with a virgin in the house east [of us]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
